Package manticore.presentation.swing.terminal

Class Summary
ConsoleInputStream Input stream that can be related to a Swing JTextPane to be the input of a terminal.
ConsoleOutputStream Byte array output stream that can be related to a Swing JTextComponent to be the output of a terminal.
ConsolePrintStream Print stream that can be related to a Swing JTextComponent to be the output of a terminal.
SwingTerminalStream Creates a two-way communication with a terminal using a Swing JTextPane for user input and output.
TerminalFilter Filters content of an input/output component to be used for terminal communication.
